{"tid":712503,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英格蘭訓練筆記曝光     史達寧後備","createTime":"2018-06-22T06:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T08:51:39.000Z","uid":4661,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"d107325c706a123f199e24e946caa35896634a51","tid":712503,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:41:49.000Z","msg":"英國傳媒周四偷拍到英軍助教賀蘭特（Steve Holland）的戰術筆記，發現領隊修夫基疑似計劃將上場頻頻失機的史達寧踢出正選之列，由拉舒福特取代其位置，而另一名正選球員迪利亞里亦會因傷缺陣。<br />\n<br />\n從英媒偷拍出來的相片顯示，修夫基每個位置似乎都選擇了正選和後備球員，其中以隊長哈利卡尼為首的正選陣容，連格、軒達臣等保住正選，另羅夫斯卓克及拉舒福特，將取代迪利亞里及史達寧的位置。<br />\n<br />\n不過以上都是英媒的猜測，或者那份戰術筆記，亦只是修夫基將球員適合的位置寫上，真正的正選陣容仍有待下場對巴拿馬前揭盅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180622/large/1529608638_1fe9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180622%2Flarge%2F1529608638_1fe9.jpg&h=7707192a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180622/large/1529608641_381f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180622%2Flarge%2F1529608641_381f.jpg&h=c9564728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180622/large/1529608644_53b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180622%2Flarge%2F1529608644_53b0.jpg&h=1cba427d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0627f4d7bf3d7309070c9b75d272befc19eec272","tid":712503,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:49:37.000Z","msg":"其實三中堅依家已經過左時，英撚兩個翼衛咁廢後防又咁撚屎、缺經驗，憑乜打三中堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b921007a854c37972591e2584fbdd48f0f1ae1","tid":712503,"uid":13667,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0627f4d7bf3d7309070c9b75d272befc19eec272","tid":712503,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:49:37.000Z","msg":"